title: Emerica's Cranberries and Coronas Tour
description:
From Oct 3rd through Oct 12th, a crew from Emerica went on a little road trip in the North Eastern USA. This is just a fraction of that trip for you. The skate footage of Leo, Brandon and Marquis will be released soon - this video is about the shops, the kids, the good times on the road. Thanks to all the skateboarders and shops for supporting Emerica!
#MadeInEmerica #EmericaG6
